additional_info:
Change background color of Disabled/Enabled status within code to whatever you want.

<code>/* Disabled */
.quickjava-button[status="0"]{
  background-color:#FF0033 !important;
}

/* Enabled */
.quickjava-button[status="1"]{
  background-color:#3399CC !important;
}</code>

css:
@namespace url(http://www.mozilla.org/keymaster/gatekeeper/there.is.only.xul);

.quickjava-button{
  font-weight: bolder !important;
  color:#FFFFFF !important;
  text-decoration:none !important;
  border:1px solid #999999 !important;
  text-align:center !important;
  margin: 1px !important;
  padding: 1px !important;
  list-style-image: url("data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==") !important;

  border-radius:5px !important;

  background-color: #999999 !important;
  background-image: url("data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABAAAAAQCAQAAAC1+jfqAAAAY0lEQVR4Xu2LuQ2AQAwEB8nd0AHV0SwnAgICDo7jtSy+wCWwIwfW7hRHTcVItLux35iEkkB8B2+lJJLQOJ5VzGSyDjyPbOygA89j4YoQHi+aucEXoTVv0FtxInSku/QHPSt/TkhiW03aPUxxAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC") !important;
  background-repeat: no-repeat !important;
}

/* Disabled */
.quickjava-button[status="0"]{
  background-color:#FF0033 !important;
}

/* Enabled */
.quickjava-button[status="1"]{
  background-color:#3399CC !important;
}

/* Hidden */
.QuickJava_StatusIcon_Container[status="-1"]{
display: none !important;
}
